### Cart API Testing
### Make sure order-service is running on port 5005
### Replace {{token}} with actual customer authentication token
### Replace {{customerId}} with actual customer ID

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5005/api/cart
@token = Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...
@menuItemId = 676040c2d6ba3f0e83ccdc92

### 1. Get Cart (Create if not exists)
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: {{token}}

### 2. Add Item to Cart
POST {{baseUrl}}/add
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "menuItemId": "{{menuItemId}}",
  "quantity": 2,
  "customizations": "Không cay",
  "notes": "Gói riêng"
}

### 3. Add Another Item
POST {{baseUrl}}/add
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "menuItemId": "676040c2d6ba3f0e83ccdc93",
  "quantity": 1,
  "customizations": "Cay vừa",
  "notes": ""
}

### 4. Get Cart Summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/summary
Authorization: {{token}}

### 5. Update Cart Item Quantity
PUT {{baseUrl}}/items/CART_ITEM_ID_HERE
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 3
}

### 6. Apply Coupon
POST {{baseUrl}}/coupon
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "couponCode": "WELCOME10"
}

### 7. Update Delivery Info
PUT {{baseUrl}}/delivery
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "delivery",
  "address": {
    "full": "123 Nguyễn Văn A, Phường 1, Quận 1, TP.HCM",
    "district": "Quận 1",
    "city": "TP.HCM"
  },
  "estimatedTime": 45
}

### 8. Remove Coupon
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/coupon
Authorization: {{token}}

### 9. Remove Item from Cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/items/CART_ITEM_ID_HERE
Authorization: {{token}}

### 10. Checkout Cart (Convert to Order)
POST {{baseUrl}}/checkout
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payment": {
    "method": "momo"
  },
  "notes": {
    "customer": "Giao hàng trước 6PM",
    "kitchen": "Không cay",
    "delivery": "Gọi trước khi giao"
  }
}

### 11. Clear Cart
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/clear
Authorization: {{token}}

### Quick Test Workflow:
### 1. Get cart → 2. Add items → 3. Apply coupon → 4. Update delivery → 5. Checkout

### Test with different menu items:
@crabId = 676040c2d6ba3f0e83ccdc94
@shrimpId = 676040c2d6ba3f0e83ccdc95
@fishId = 676040c2d6ba3f0e83ccdc96

### Add Crab
POST {{baseUrl}}/add
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "menuItemId": "{{crabId}}",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Add Shrimp
POST {{baseUrl}}/add
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "menuItemId": "{{shrimpId}}",
  "quantity": 3
}

### Test Error Cases:

### Invalid menu item ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/add
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "menuItemId": "invalid_id",
  "quantity": 1
}

### Quantity too high
POST {{baseUrl}}/add
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "menuItemId": "{{menuItemId}}",
  "quantity": 100
}

### Invalid coupon
POST {{baseUrl}}/coupon
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "couponCode": "INVALID_COUPON"
}
